## 🌟 About the Author

**Jeremy Darling** is an Engineering Manager at US Bank and an advocate for mental health and empathetic leadership. His talks blend his technical expertise in distributed systems with his passion for fostering human connection in professional settings. Jeremy's goal is to empower managers to lead with compassion, especially when navigating sensitive or challenging workplace events.

---

